Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban is a 2004 action-adventure video game. The game is based on the 2004 film of the same name from the Harry Potter franchise. The game was released as a trio, with separate versions for Game Boy Advance, Microsoft Windows, and home consoles (released on PlayStation 2, Xbox, and GameCube).
